]}]},{"data":{"id":"dikn33y5jag0","created":1778989330219,"text":"基于多智能体协同的分离装置全局自动设计框架","priority":6},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dikn4jwq2l40","created":1778989443326,"text":"多物理场智能体协同机制与工作流调度","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dikn4yskp740","created":1778989475726,"text":" 明确气动、动力、结构、分离四个专属智能体的工作顺序与数据交互规则。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dikn4nhffyg0","created":1778989451108,"text":"跨领域设计冲突化解与全局参数平衡","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dikn4vxggew0","created":1778989469491,"text":"解决不同智能体优化目标相互矛盾的问题。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dikn52i9osw0","created":1778989483810,"text":"智能化自动设计全流程推演与效能验证","expandState":"collapse"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dikn55uh9m80","created":1778989491079,"text":"输入一个真实的极端复合边界工况，驱动这套多智能体系统从头到尾自动执行一轮设计寻优。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dikmyyyd9ug0","created":1778989005892,"text":"绪论","layout_right_offset":{"x":11,"y":-974},"priority":1},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dikmz4mpnqo0","created":1778989018248,"text":"总结与展望","priority":7},"children":[]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fish","version":"1.4.43"}